@startuml Warehouse Digital Twin Architecture
!theme mars
skinparam backgroundColor #0f0f23
skinparam defaultFontColor #e2e8f0
skinparam componentBackgroundColor #1a1a2e
skinparam componentBorderColor #4a5568
skinparam databaseBackgroundColor #2d3748
skinparam nodeBackgroundColor #1e293b
skinparam noteBorderColor #4a5568
skinparam arrowColor #63b3ed
skinparam stereotypeFontColor #a0aec0
skinparam packageBorderColor #4a5568
skinparam rectangleBorderColor #4a5568
skinparam rectangleBackgroundColor #1e293b
skinparam cloudBorderColor #4a5568
skinparam cloudBackgroundColor #1a1a2e


title **Warehouse Digital Twin — System Architecture**\nBrev GPU cloud + optional local split · All-in-one (brev-compose.yml) or split (brev-compose-phase4.yml + local-compose.yml)\nROS 2 Jazzy · Domain ID 42 · FastDDS (SHM disabled, UDP only) · RMW: rmw_fastrtps_cpp

' ============================================================================
' BREV CLOUD GPU INSTANCE
' ============================================================================

cloud "**Brev Cloud GPU Instance**\nUbuntu 22.04 · L40S GPU · NVIDIA 580 · CUDA 13.0\nAll containers: network_mode: host" as brev_cloud #1a1a3e {

    rectangle "**discovery-server**\nros:jazzy\n---\nfast-discovery-server -i 0 -p 11811\n(NOT fastdds discovery subcommand)\nUDP 0.0.0.0:**11811**\nHealthcheck: grep -q 2E23 /proc/net/udp\n//Central DDS discovery for all ROS 2 nodes//" as discovery #2b6cb0

    rectangle "**isaac-sim-init**\nnvcr.io/nvidia/isaac-sim:**5.1.0**\n---\nOne-shot init container (runs as root)\nchown named volumes to uid 1234\n//Volume permission bootstrap//" as init #4a5568

    rectangle "**isaac-sim**\nnvcr.io/nvidia/isaac-sim:**5.1.0**\n---\nKit streaming container (headless)\nEntrypoint: runheadless.sh → isaac-sim.streaming.sh\nCommand: --exec \"warehouse_scene_streaming.py\"\n---\n**PhysX Engine:**\n  TGS solver · GPU dynamics · GPU broadphase\n  CCD + stabilization · 60 Hz (16.67ms)\n  Z-up gravity (0,0,-9.81)\nLoads: scene_assembly.usd\n---\n**WebRTC Streaming:**\n  Signal port: 49100 · Stream port: 47998\n**Healthcheck:** test -f /tmp/isaac-sim-ready\nstart_period: 300s (shader compilation)\n---\n**Volumes:** isaac-sim-cache, logs, data, config\n//Physics truth source + rendering//" as isaacsim #553c9a

    rectangle "**OmniGraph ROS 2 Bridge**\n(inside isaac-sim · one graph per forklift)" as omnigraph #7b3f9e {
        component "OnPlaybackTick (60 Hz)" as tick
        component "ROS2PublishClock → /clock" as clock_pub
        component "ROS2SubscribeTwist\n→ cmd_vel_bridge_loop\n→ IsaacArticulationController ×2\n  (drive + steer per forklift)" as twist_pipeline
        component "IsaacComputeOdometry\n→ ROS2PublishOdometry" as odom_pipeline
    }

    rectangle "**vehicle-controller**\nCustom image (ros:jazzy)\n---\nForkliftControllerNode (**×4** via launch)\nmulti_forklift.launch.py\nNUM_FORKLIFTS env → spawns N nodes\n---\n**Control loop:** 10 Hz timer\n**Status broadcast:** 2 Hz timer\n**Navigation:** P-controller (Phase 1)\nKP_LINEAR=0.5 · KP_ANGULAR=2.0\n---\n**Fork heights (m):**\nGROUND=0.0 · TRAVEL=0.5 · LIFTED=0.8\n**Wheel:** r=0.15m · dist=1.0m\n**Limits:** 0.5 m/s · 1.0 rad/s\n//State machine drives forklifts//" as vehicle #38a169

    rectangle "**web-viewer**\nStatic Vite site (WebRTC client)\nport **8210**\n---\nConnects to isaac-sim streaming\nServes browser-based 3D view\n//Optional 3D viewer//" as webviewer #4a5568
}

' ============================================================================
' ALL-IN-ONE OR LOCAL SERVICES
' ============================================================================

cloud "**Orchestration & UI Services**\n(brev-compose.yml all-in-one, or local-compose.yml split)\nCan run on Brev (host network) or local machine\nLocal: fastdds_client_resolved.xml via envsubst" as local_machine #1e293b {

    rectangle "**warehouse-manager**\nCustom image (ros:jazzy + FastAPI)\nWarehouseManagerNode · uvicorn port **8000**\n---\n**REST API:**\nPOST /orders · GET /orders?status=\nGET /forklifts · GET /forklifts/{id}\nPUT /forklifts/{id}/pause · /resume\nDELETE /tasks/{task_id}\nGET /metrics · POST /config\nPOST /reset\nPOST /record/start · /record/stop\nPOST /replay/start · /replay/stop\n---\n**WebSocket** /ws/live:\nsnapshot (on connect) · forklift_update\norder_update · task_status · reset\n---\n**ROS 2 Node** (spins in bg thread):\nSubscribes: /{id}/status, /warehouse/task_status\nPublishes: /warehouse/task_assignment\nuse_sim_time=true\n//Central orchestrator//" as manager #c05621

    rectangle "**Dispatcher** (dispatcher.py)" as dispatch #8b4513 {
        component "nearest_assign()\n//Greedy closest idle forklift\n(Euclidean distance)//" as nearest
        component "batch_assign()\n//Hungarian algorithm\n(scipy linear_sum_assignment)\nOptimal cost-matrix assignment//" as hungarian
    }

    rectangle "**Scenario Engine** (scenario.py)" as scenario_engine #6b4226 {
        component "ScenarioRecorder\n//Records order events with\nms-offset timestamps//" as scenario_rec
        component "save/load Scenario\n//JSON files in scenarios/ dir//" as scenario_io
    }

    database "**redis**\nredis:7-alpine · port **6379**\nAOF persistence\n---\nIn-memory state cache\nPub/Sub event relay\n**Volume:** redis-data\nHealthcheck: redis-cli ping\n//Hot state layer//" as redis #c53030

    database "**SQLite**\nwarehouse.db · WAL mode\nbusy_timeout=5000\n---\n**orders** (id, items JSON, priority,\n  status, assigned_forklift,\n  created_at, completed_at)\n**tasks** (id, order_id, forklift_id,\n  status, shelf_x/y/z, dock_x/y/z,\n  created_at, completed_at)\n**metrics_log** (timestamp,\n  metric_name, metric_value, strategy)\n**Volume:** warehouse-db\n//Persistent history//" as sqlite #718096

    rectangle "**dashboard**\nReact 18 + TypeScript · Vite\nport **3000** (Nginx in prod) · profile: dashboard\n---\n**Components:**\nWarehouseMap (Konva 2D canvas)\nFleetStatus (4 forklift cards 2×2)\nOrderQueue (sortable table)\nMetricsPanel (KPI cards + Recharts)\nConfigPanel (dispatch strategy radio)\n---\n**State:** Zustand stores\nwarehouseStore · orderStore · metricsStore\n**Hooks:** useApi() · useWebSocket()\nAuto-reconnect WS (1s–10s backoff)\n---\nVITE_API_URL · VITE_WS_URL\n//Browser UI//" as dashboard #2b6cb0
}

' ============================================================================
' FORKLIFT STATE MACHINE
' ============================================================================

rectangle "**Forklift State Machine** (ForkliftControllerNode · per forklift)" as fsm #2d3748 {
    rectangle "IDLE (0)" as s_idle #38a169
    rectangle "NAVIGATING_TO_SHELF (1)" as s_nav_shelf #2b6cb0
    rectangle "PICKING (2)" as s_pick #ecc94b
    rectangle "NAVIGATING_TO_DOCK (3)" as s_nav_dock #2b6cb0
    rectangle "DROPPING (4)" as s_drop #ecc94b
    rectangle "ERROR (5)" as s_error #e53e3e
    rectangle "RECOVERING (6)" as s_recover #ed8936

    s_idle -[#68d391]-> s_nav_shelf : TaskAssignment\nreceived
    s_nav_shelf -[#68d391]-> s_pick : distance < 0.3m\nto shelf
    s_pick -[#68d391]-> s_nav_dock : pick sequence\ncomplete (~6s)
    s_nav_dock -[#68d391]-> s_drop : distance < 0.3m\nto dock
    s_drop -[#68d391]-> s_idle : drop sequence\ncomplete (~5s)\npublish TaskStatus=completed
    s_nav_shelf -[#fc8181,dashed]-> s_error : timeout/stuck
    s_nav_dock -[#fc8181,dashed]-> s_error : timeout/stuck
    s_error -[#ed8936,dashed]-> s_recover : auto-recovery
    s_recover -[#68d391,dashed]-> s_idle : recovered
}

' ============================================================================
' WAREHOUSE SCENE LAYOUT
' ============================================================================

rectangle "**Warehouse Scene** (scene_assembly.usd)" as scene_layout #2d3748 {
    rectangle "/World/warehouse\n//Environment mesh//" as env_mesh #4a5568
    rectangle "/World/forklift_0..3\n//4 articulated forklifts\nCloned from /World/forklift_b\nSpawns: (-15,-25) (-5,-25)\n(5,-25) (15,-25)//" as forklifts_scene #38a169
    rectangle "/World/Rack_A..D\n//4 shelf racks at Y≈10m\nBox collision prims//" as racks #ecc94b
    rectangle "/World/Dock_1..2\n//2 loading docks at Y≈-32m//" as docks #2b6cb0
    rectangle "/World/pick_box_0\n//Test rigid body cube\n0.4m at (5,10,0.6)//" as pickbox #a0aec0
}

' ============================================================================
' CONNECTIONS — NETWORK (cross-host when split)
' ============================================================================

brev_cloud <-[#ecc94b,bold]-> local_machine : **DDS over UDP**\n(Tailscale VPN when split deploy)\nfastdds_no_shm.xml: SHM disabled

' ============================================================================
' CONNECTIONS — FASTDDS DISCOVERY
' ============================================================================

discovery -[#63b3ed,dashed]-> isaacsim : DDS register\n(multicast or SERVER)
discovery -[#63b3ed,dashed]-> vehicle : DDS register
discovery .[#63b3ed,dashed].> manager : DDS register\n(CLIENT mode when split)

' ============================================================================
' CONNECTIONS — INIT → VOLUMES
' ============================================================================

init -[#a0aec0,dashed]-> isaacsim : chown volumes\n(service_completed_successfully)

' ============================================================================
' CONNECTIONS — OMNIGRAPH INTERNAL
' ============================================================================

tick --> clock_pub
tick --> twist_pipeline
tick --> odom_pipeline

' ============================================================================
' CONNECTIONS — BREV-INTERNAL DDS (isaac-sim ↔ vehicle-controller)
' ============================================================================

vehicle -[#68d391]-> twist_pipeline : /{id}/cmd_vel (Twist)\n10 Hz
odom_pipeline -[#68d391]-> vehicle : /{id}/odom (Odometry)\n60 Hz
vehicle -[#68d391]-> isaacsim : /{id}/fork_cmd (Float64)
clock_pub -[#a0aec0,dashed]-> vehicle : /clock (Clock)\n60 Hz

' ============================================================================
' CONNECTIONS — DDS (vehicle-controller ↔ warehouse-manager)
' ============================================================================

manager -[#68d391,bold]-> vehicle : /warehouse/task_assignment\n(TaskAssignment.msg)\nRELIABLE · VOLATILE
vehicle -[#fc8181,bold]-> manager : /{id}/status (ForkliftStatus.msg)\nRELIABLE · 2 Hz
vehicle -[#fc8181,bold]-> manager : /warehouse/task_status\n(TaskStatus.msg) · RELIABLE

' ============================================================================
' CONNECTIONS — DATA STORES
' ============================================================================

manager -[#a0aec0]-> redis : cache state\nPub/Sub events
manager -[#a0aec0]-> sqlite : persist orders, tasks,\nmetrics history
manager -[#a0aec0]-> dispatch : _try_dispatch()\ncurrent_strategy variable
manager -[#a0aec0]-> scenario_engine : record/replay\norder events

' ============================================================================
' CONNECTIONS — DASHBOARD ↔ MANAGER
' ============================================================================

dashboard -[#63b3ed]-> manager : **REST** GET/POST/PUT/DELETE\nhttp://localhost:8000
manager -[#63b3ed]-> dashboard : **WebSocket** /ws/live\nJSON frames:\nsnapshot · forklift_update\norder_update · task_status · reset

' ============================================================================
' CONNECTIONS — WEB VIEWER
' ============================================================================

webviewer -[#a0aec0,dashed]-> isaacsim : WebRTC stream\nports 49100 / 47998

' ============================================================================
' ROS 2 CUSTOM MESSAGE TYPES
' ============================================================================

legend right
  **ROS 2 Topic Map**
  |= Topic |= Type |= QoS |= Rate |= Direction |
  | /warehouse/task_assignment | warehouse_msgs/TaskAssignment | RELIABLE/VOLATILE | on dispatch | Mgr→Ctrl |
  | /{id}/status | warehouse_msgs/ForkliftStatus | RELIABLE | 2 Hz | Ctrl→Mgr |
  | /warehouse/task_status | warehouse_msgs/TaskStatus | RELIABLE | on event | Ctrl→Mgr |
  | /{id}/cmd_vel | geometry_msgs/Twist | BEST_EFFORT | 10 Hz | Ctrl→Sim |
  | /{id}/fork_cmd | std_msgs/Float64 | BEST_EFFORT | on event | Ctrl→Sim |
  | /{id}/odom | nav_msgs/Odometry | BEST_EFFORT | 60 Hz | Sim→Ctrl |
  | /clock | rosgraph_msgs/Clock | -- | 60 Hz | Sim→All |

  **Custom Message Definitions (warehouse_msgs)**
  |= Message |= Fields |
  | ForkliftStatus.msg | forklift_id, state (uint8), pose, battery_level, current_task_id, stamp |
  | TaskAssignment.msg | task_id, forklift_id, order_id, shelf_position, dock_position, priority, stamp |
  | TaskStatus.msg | task_id, forklift_id, status (string), detail, stamp |
  | OrderStatus.msg | order_id, status, items[], assigned_forklift, stamp |
  | ResetSimulation.srv | clear_orders → success, message |

  **Arrow Legend**
  |= Color |= Meaning |
  | <#68d391> | ROS 2 DDS publish (control data) |
  | <#fc8181> | ROS 2 DDS publish (status feedback) |
  | <#63b3ed> | HTTP / WebSocket |
  | <#a0aec0> | Internal / telemetry / infra (dashed) |
  | <#ecc94b> | Network boundary (bold) |
endlegend

' ============================================================================
' NOTES
' ============================================================================

note right of brev_cloud
  **Brev-side** (GPU-bound workloads)
  - Requires NVIDIA GPU (L40S / A4000+)
  - All containers: network_mode: host
  - ROS 2 Jazzy (all containers)
  - FastDDS SHM disabled everywhere
  - NUM_FORKLIFTS=1..4 via environment
  - **Named volumes:** isaac-sim-cache, logs, data, config
  - **Startup order (depends_on + health):**
    1. isaac-sim-init (volume permissions)
    2. discovery-server (UDP port 11811)
    3. isaac-sim (scene load + shader compile)
    4. web-viewer (depends_on: isaac-sim healthy)
    5. vehicle-controller
end note

note right of local_machine
  **Orchestration side** (no GPU required)
  - Runs on Brev (all-in-one) or local machine (split)
  - **All-in-one** (brev-compose.yml):
    All services on single Brev host
  - **Split** (local-compose.yml + Makefile):
    1. make up → envsubst + docker compose
    2. make dashboard → optional profile
    3. Connects to Brev via BREV_TAILSCALE_IP
  - **Volumes:** warehouse-db, redis-data
  - **Env:** BREV_TAILSCALE_IP, ROS_DOMAIN_ID=42,
    DISPATCH_STRATEGY, DATABASE_PATH, REDIS_URL
end note

note bottom of fsm
  **Pick sequence (~6s, timed — not sensor-based):**
  1. Lower fork to GROUND (2s)
  2. Drive forward 0.1 m/s (2s)
  3. Raise fork to LIFTED (2s)
  **Drop sequence (~5s, timed):**
  1. Lower fork to GROUND (2s)
  2. Reverse -0.1 m/s (2s)
  3. Raise fork to TRAVEL (1s)
  //Phase 1: P-controller, no Nav2, no sensors//
  //Battery: hardcoded 100.0 (simulation only)//
end note

note right of omnigraph
  **OmniGraph Node Types (Isaac Sim 5.1.0):**
  omni.graph.action.OnPlaybackTick
  isaacsim.ros2.bridge.ROS2PublishClock
  isaacsim.ros2.bridge.ROS2SubscribeTwist
  isaacsim.core.nodes.IsaacComputeOdometry
  isaacsim.ros2.bridge.ROS2PublishOdometry
  isaacsim.core.nodes.IsaacReadSimulationTime
  isaacsim.core.nodes.IsaacArticulationController ×2
  ---
  **cmd_vel Bridge (Python frame loop):**
  twist_sub outputs → DRIVE_SCALE (-1/0.15 ≈ -6.667)
  → drive ArticulationController (rad/s)
  twist_sub angular → STEER_SCALE (20°)
  → steer ArticulationController (rad)
  STEER_MAX = 30° · Runs every physics frame
end note

' ============================================================================
' HAPPY PATH — ORDER LIFECYCLE
' ============================================================================

note bottom of manager
  **Order Lifecycle (happy path):**
  1. Dashboard → POST /orders → DB insert
  2. WebSocket broadcast: order_update
  3. _try_dispatch() → Dispatcher selects forklift
  4. Publish TaskAssignment.msg via ROS 2
  5. Controller: IDLE → NAVIGATING_TO_SHELF
  6. P-control loop at 10 Hz (cmd_vel)
  7. PICKING (timed) → NAVIGATING_TO_DOCK
  8. DROPPING (timed) → IDLE
  9. Controller publishes TaskStatus (completed)
  10. Manager updates DB + WebSocket broadcast
  11. Dashboard reflects completion
end note

@enduml
